=\"hkgmoji\" />:急吖嘛"},{"pid":"6f07c2c75ac32a321de05aba56cf57af6a31ccdd","tid":1023893,"uid":15813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T07:45:11.000Z","msg":"包容呀！你屎不屎蚛蟈撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1afeaa383ca48324d7f75b3c7d9f4058bcc2e930","tid":1023893,"uid":51509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:06:21.000Z","msg":"中國細路係北京紫禁城隨地小便中國網民就唔包容<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國細路係香港隨地小便中國網民就話要包容<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果話中國網民覺得自己地方唔可以俾細路隨地小便嘅話<br />\n咁中國網民當北京係自己地方嘅時候有冇當香港係自己地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國網民係咪搞港獨分裂國家主權<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a47fdbaec3a3f73a136be51f9facf1116faed8f","tid":1023893,"uid":65201,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:11:50.000Z","msg":"講真等咁耐急都係人之常情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係搵個地方解決姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到人陸人就唔埋三七廿一屌左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比人叫兒登唔係無原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee0f4a8baed0b7fc98372e44b8ad31a1e325fb4","tid":1023893,"uid":60140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a47fdbaec3a3f73a136be51f9facf1116faed8f","tid":1023893,"uid":65201,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:11:50.000Z","msg":"講真等咁耐急都係人之常情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係搵個地方解決姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到人陸人就唔埋三七廿一屌左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比人叫兒登唔係無原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:26:29.000Z","msg":"急就要即刻